title: SC EP:83 Sasquatch encounter on the mountain
itunes:title: SC EP:83 Sasquatch encounter on the mountain
description: Tonight we speak to Alex who had an encounter as a young man during a hiking expedition. Years later he had another encounter while skiing. These encounters have changed his life. Alex discusses the behaviors and what he saw.
